            <title><![CDATA[산불에 ‘속’타는 캘리포니아, 이번엔 바다에 ‘검은 기름띠’]]></title>
            <link>https://www.khan.co.kr/world/america/article/202110042116005/?utm_campaign=list_click&amp;utm_source=reporter_article&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=%EB%B0%95%EC%9D%80%ED%95%98_%EA%B8%B0%EC%9E%90%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80</link>
